  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Un darrija to par Kehnixu\npahr Gileadu/un pahr teem Affu-\nritexeem/ un pahr Jefreelu/ un\npahr Gewrāimu/un pahr Benja-\nminu/ un pahr wiſſu Israēlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Tschetrdesmits Gaddus\nwezz bija Jsboſets Saula Dehls/\nkad wiſch Kehnisch ktua pahr\nIsraelu/ un waldtja diwi Gad-\ndus/ bet tee no ta Naimma Juḥ-\nda turrejahs pee Dahwida.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un wiſſ tas Laiks/ tamehr\nDahwids Kehnisch bijis Gebro-\nnā pahr to Naimmu Juha/ irr\nſeptini Gaddi un ſechti Mehnechi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Tad iṣgahje Abners Nera\nDehls/ ar Jsboſeta Saula Deh-\nla Kalpeein/ no Maānaim us Gi-\nbeonu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Un Joabs Jerujas Dehls\niṣgahje arridsan ar Dahwida Kal-\npeem/ un fastappahs weens oh-\ntru pee Gibcoxa Dihkt/ un tee\npalikke / ſchis ſchaipuſſ Dihka/\nun tas ohtrs wiannpuſſ Dihka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Un Abners faẓẓija us Jo-\nabu: Lai jelle tee Puifchi zelkahs/\nun muhsu Breekcha ſpehle/ tad\nfaẓẓija Joabs: Teem buhs zeltees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Tad zehlehs/ un nogahje\ndiwipadeſnits Pulka no Benja-\nmina preekſch Jsboſetu Saula\nDehlu/ un diwipadeſnits no\nDahwida Kalpeeim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Un weens grabbe to ohtru\npee Galwas/ un eedubre ſawn\nSohbinu ohtram Sahnōs/ un\ntee kritte wiſſi lihds/ un ſchi Wee-\nta tappe nosankta Eſkat- Azu-\nrin/ kas Gibeonā irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Un tai Deena tappe gruh-\nta Raufchana/ bet Abners un\nfraēta Wihrī tappe preeſſch Dah-\nwida Kalpeeim kauti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Un tur btja trihſ Deh-\nJerujas/ Joabs/ un Abisajus un\nAsaēts. Un Asaēts bija weegli-\nus fawahm Kahjahni/ ittin ka-\nweena Stirna Lanka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Un Asaēts dsinnahs Ab-\nneram pakkat/ un ne atstabjah-\nno Abnera/ nei pa labbo Rohk-\nnei pa kreifo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Un Abners faṭṭijahs ap-\nkahrt/ un faẓẓija : Neggi tu ef-\nAsaēts? un wiſch faẓẓija : E-\nesimu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Tad faẓẓija Abners uṣto-\nAtkahpees/ jeb pa labbo Rohk-\njeb pa kreifo Rohku/ un nemu-\npreeſſch tewis weenu no tee-\nPuifscheen/un nemunees ſew wi-\nna Eerohtschus : Bet Asaēts ni-\ngribbeja no wiṣṣa atſtaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Tad runnaja Abners wes-\nus Asaēln/ un faẓẓija : Atka-\npees no manntin/ ſapehz buh-\nman tew feimme kaut? ka wa-\nreſchu es tad fatwu Waign po-\nzelt preeſſch tawu Brahli Joabu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Bet wiſch leedſehs a-\nkahytees. Tad duhre Abner-\nwizzu ar ta Schkehpa ohtr-\nGallu Kungi/ ka tas Schkeh-\npakkat iṣgahje/ un Asaēts fri-\ntur/ un nomirre tai Weetā/ u-\nwiffi/ kas us to Weetu nahze-\nkur Asaēts btja krittis un nomi-\nris/ tee pastahweja tur.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "24. Bet Joabs un Abisaj-\ndsū\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
